 <purpose>
   The External_class application module supports the requirement to
   identify classes that are defined external to a data exchange file in a
   External Class Library.
 </purpose>

 <inscope>
   <li>
     The identification of a class that is external to a data exchange file;
   </li>
   <li>
     The identification of an external class library that is not in an
     exchange file and holds the definition for classes used in the
     exchange file;
   </li>
   <li>
     A reference to a class in an external class library.
   </li>
 </inscope>

 <outscope>
   <li>
     The definition of a class;
   </li>
   <li>
     The definition of an external class library.
   </li>
 </outscope>


